Subject: [PATCH 0037/1141] ARM: dts: stm32: use i2c6 scmi clock on stm32mp15
 family

On STM32MP15 soc, I2C4 and I2C6 share the same clock. So if I2C4 clock is
handled by SCMI, I2C6 should be handled by SCMI too.

